Following a clean sweep by chairperson Stan Mathabatha, as he was elected for a third term, the ANC Limpopo elective conference is to come to a close today. President Cyril Ramaphosa is expected to deliver the closing address in Polokwane. POLOKWANE - President Cyril Ramaphosa addresses the closing of the ANC LimpopoÂ Conference.
Stan Mathabatha has been re-elected as the ANC Limpopo provincial chairperson.
He retains the position for a third term. Mathabatha says all ANC members must rally behind the selected leaders.